{"tid":202714,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人睇緊明珠台 ARGO – 救參任務","createTime":"2017-04-15T16:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T01:27:44.000Z","uid":4260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b03a3fe59d257191928c98818125557565f1b0a","tid":202714,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"0025 - 0300<br />\n<br />\n今晚明珠做argo，翡翠做套神探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45ff3aef9e9ddf8a2df5e5faa6a3b00b3f3ca3ff","tid":202714,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>0025 - 0300<br />\n<br />\n今晚明珠做argo，翡翠做<del>套</del>神探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"579024e3efbad61dfdea8fec3b389e086f354768","tid":202714,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:07:08.000Z","msg":"故事講乜架？"},{"pid":"9b215d9325f1322448adcc011d5f4d7c6cbd6e6c","tid":202714,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:12:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>故事講乜架？</blockquote><br />\n《ARGO &ndash; 救參任務》由《狂盜之城》、《驕陽似我》奧斯卡得主賓艾佛力自導自演，《油激暗戰》金像男星佐治古尼、《各位觀眾，晚安》奧斯卡提名監製格蘭特軒斯洛夫及賓艾佛力聯合監製。<br />\n<br />\n1979年11月4日，伊朗的伊斯蘭革命正鬧得沸騰，激進分子衝擊駐德克蘭的美國領使館，並帶走52名美國人質。在混亂當中，六名美國人成功逃脫，並得到加拿大領使的庇護。但激進分子找出、並殺害這六名美國人只是時間問題，中情局營救專家東尼曼迪斯 (賓艾佛力 飾) 設計出一個驚險的計劃讓他們安全徹離。這個營救行動巧妙得只可能在電影中發生。"},{"pid":"e1f0a1526101f150c0d6ee4740c0f6b2412e0c2d","tid":202714,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:16:24.000Z","msg":"Ben Affleck真係好勁 又編又導又做到演員"},{"pid":"b50349f1475cb0e1cd8c618b567c928c96c0d31a","tid":202714,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ben Affleck真係好勁 又編又導又做到演員</blockquote><br />\n肥ben做編導&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;做戲"},{"pid":"d7e54afa568d1ad9deac2442ec468fe01719fc2c","tid":202714,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0